data.name: BrowseForFolderButton.ToolTip
data.value: Click here to browse for and select one or more files that you want to convert. You can also drag a whole folder or one or more file over the form to add them to the conversion list.

data.name: ShowSettingsMangerButton.ToolTip
data.value: Use this button to show the standard settings (INI) files dialog (just like in TagEditor).

data.name: ConvertButton.ToolTip
data.value: Click to start the conversion of the source files.

data.name: FilterManagerButton.ToolTip
data.value: Use this button to invoke the standard Filters dialog where you can configure filter settings.

data.name: SourceLangCombo.ToolTip
data.value: Use this drop-down list to select the source language.

data.name: ClearFilesListboxLink.ToolTip
data.value: Clears the selected files list in memory as well as the contents of the textbox below.

data.name: ClearLogLink.ToolTip
data.value: Clears the all text from the log textbox (the bottom one).

data.name: SaveLogToTextFile.ToolTip
data.value: Opens a save dialog so that you can save the contents of the log textbox to a text file.
